<item>
            <title>[OAK-3305] Self recovering instance may not see all changes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-3305</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a DocumentNodeStore instance is killed and restarted, the _lastRev recovery mechanism is triggered on startup. It may happen that the restarted instance does not see all changes that were recovered.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12859572">OAK-3305</key>
            <summary>Self recovering instance may not see all changes</summary>
